<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后希望国王发布公告。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，国王就把金盘子的事告诉全国的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在！我们需要一位勇敢的英雄去拯救公主，”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人自愿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是没有人自愿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>时间一天天过去，公主的病情越来越严重了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子终于回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当看到王国里的公告时，他激动极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！我终于能做点儿什么了！”王子心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“虽然我会失去生命，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是如果没有公主，我也活不下去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就在死前去见她最后一面吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子又穿上仆人的衣服，然后急忙向王宫走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王盯着面前这个英俊的仆人：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我你想要什么，年轻人？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想当软木塞。”王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王惊讶得站了起来：“什么？你愿意当英雄吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！我愿意献出我的生命，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让湖水重新回来。”王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那要不要先去看看你的父母？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用了。”王子说，“但我有一个条件。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么都行！”国王说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会爬进洞里，”王子开始说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，水会慢慢回到湖里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当水超过我的头时，我就会被淹死。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王低下头：“恐怕是的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个过程需要很长时间。”王子继续说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”国王咬着嘴唇，“等待是最难的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是如果你愿意当软木塞，湖水就再也不会流失了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望公主能陪着我。”王子接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂我吃东西、陪我聊聊天，安慰安慰我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等水到我的眼睛时，公主就可以离开了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我答应你的条件！”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在就去准备吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的侍卫们会去寻找那个洞的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>侍卫们花了很长时间找啊找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他们终于在湖底的中心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>找到了那个在巨石中的洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>侍卫们急忙回去告诉国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是时候拯救湖水和公主了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>